sub_title: DHL Supply Chain - General Manager Tiel1
summary: Starting, developing and leading warehouses, full supply chains and large scale operations. 10 years+ experience in large, dynamic and fast growing e-commerce environments. Creates cross functional teams to solve complex problems by its source. Its my purpose to create an open an cooperational environment for both employees as customers. With a passion for leadership, learning and process development I create results for today and the future.
